com.gcell.ibeacon.gcellbeaconscanlibrary

Class GCellBeaconRegion

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.gcell.ibeacon.gcellbeaconscanlibrary.GCellBeaconRegion

  • public class GCellBeaconRegion
extends java.lang.Object
    Created by ibeacon on 06/04/16. Class represents a Beacon Region. A region can be defined by its UUID, its UUID + a Major number or by its UUID + Major number + Minor Number. If using the GCellBeaconScanLibrary useBeaconRegions then only beacons in Range and within a defined region will be returned.
